   "source": [
    "### Prompt for ``powershel`` or ``cmd`` to create the folder:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f8501639",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "``mkdir`` myproject"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5ac8f30c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Prompt to access the folder"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "aa7be892",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "``cd`` myproject"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "09831d09",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Now that we are in the correct folder, we can initialize Git on that folder:\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "00a3e5ca",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "git init"
   ]
  }
 ],
